==Snake Weed==
===Searching the Marshy jungle vine===
* {{mes|You search the vine...}}
* {{tbox|pic=Grimy snake weed detail.png|You find a herb.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Trufitus===
* '''Trufitus:''' Hello Bwana, do you have the Snake Weed?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Of course!}}
** '''Player:''' Of course!
** {{tcond|If the player does not have any snake weed:}}
*** '''Trufitus:''' Please don't try to deceive me.
*** '''Trufitus:''' I really need that Snake Weed if I am to make this potion.
