*** '''Trufitus:''' To the east you will find a small peninsula, it is just after the cliffs come down to meet the sands, here is where you should search for it.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has snake weed, but obtained from a monster drop:}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Snake weed detail.png|You give the Snake Weed to Trufitus.}}
